.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/9130/', '', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 'Diamorphine, Acamprosate, Lofexidine, Naltrexone, Varenicline, Levacetylmethadol, Nalmefene, Nicotine, Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, Pentazocine, More', 1767369485);
